title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Toolbar Pushback
description:
In this video we will have a look at the Toolbar Pushback created by AmbitiousPilots and is available for free on flightsim.to. The tool can be used to manage the pushback of the aircraft but in addition can be used to ask things like the baggage truck, fuel truck and opening the different doors of the aircraft  The current version of the aircraft is version 1.0.1

If you would like to try Toolbar Pushback yourself download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/15033/toolbar-pushback
